{"tid":1591800,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"幫位義士整好既iphone 6無背光（義士免費整iphone)","createTime":"2019-09-24T10:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:16:59.000Z","uid":320119,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"66c8080ac90a01d0e7172ddccac156bb20e828d5","tid":1591800,"uid":320119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"我p牌推唔到po，唔知我係邊個既巴絲可以睇番舊post：<br />\n專門整iPhone壞主板之你問我答（義士免費整iPhone)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義士比我整果陣話係唔著機<br />\n其實唔係唔著機，係有顯示無背光，背光電路問題<br />\nIphone 6整背光可以話係最麻煩最考功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkrZdup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkrZdup.jpg&h=67ca2247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開機果陣打斜用光照住佢可以好隱約見到蘋果logo <br />\n說明係背光電路問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akNYt39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakNYt39.jpg&h=056ba996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上係顯微鏡既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆塊板出黎，見到背光電路既二極管已經燒穿，電感有發黃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBN9AKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBN9AKM.jpg&h=f08eecb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上都係顯微鏡既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要換哂成組電子元件，拆既時候好考功夫，因為係正cpu格離<br />\n溫度稍高少少或者時間稍長少少cpu都會因受唔住高溫GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCOEdxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCOEdxx.jpg&h=1b9541da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小心翼翼咁拆左電感，二極管同三粒電容出黎<br />\n比大家睇下佢地既實際大小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cchNnrJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcchNnrJ.jpg&h=157d8110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n換上好既電感，二極管，三粒電容<br />\n有番背光了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同大家粗略講下呢個背光電路既原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/24/175336_a2454b50825e65892c5322df9f6db61a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F24%2F175336_a2454b50825e65892c5322df9f6db61a.jpeg&h=fd014fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個mon需要16v電壓，而我地既電池只有4.2v，所以需要呢組升壓電路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.首先，充電ic比個4.2v既電去升壓電感<br />\n2.電感電生磁磁生電既原理，將電壓升到16v<br />\n3.背光ic控制電生磁磁生電既時間<br />\n4.經過二極管，將16v既電儲存係3粒儲能電容<br />\n5.三粒電容就可以穩定持續咁提供16v比我地個mon<br />\n<br />\n今次壞既原因係電容短路直接接地做成大電流，燒穿埋電感同二極管<br />\n所以要成組元件換哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個背光電路整左我3個鍾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好麻煩，但最後成功幫到巴打，而巴打又好開心，個感覺真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲搵我整機可以tg或ig聯絡我，<span style=\"color: red;\">一律免費</span><br />\nIg: iPhonemotherboardhk <br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FIphoneMotherboardhk&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=5e5782dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk</a>"},{"pid":"433d2524b74ff2ff0989af827d1036d69359343f","tid":1591800,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"5b542cd4eb79f5d1f23c8b2b647dd02e77688b72","tid":1591800,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd1aa1df1524167c50c024760b16013fed447116","tid":1591800,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41e97b2ee191fb248a41a785ad5341965fc6ae0","tid":1591800,"uid":274942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"巴打好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你嘅付出, 好人一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352dabd5a0f39439591f6d94191d826f452f6da2","tid":1591800,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63d966c54629b37aab14d285601dcb28fae0adb","tid":1591800,"uid":49695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"巴打讀ee?"},{"pid":"5160af435644f0d2e3764959d1f780571367ec1b","tid":1591800,"uid":320119,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b63d966c54629b37aab14d285601dcb28fae0adb","tid":1591800,"uid":49695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime